                section.kickstarter
                    .container
                        .kickstarter__body
                            .kickstarter__icon
                                img(src="/assets/img/kickstarter.png", alt="kickstarter-icon")
                            h3.kickstarter__title="Kickstarter Campain"
                            p.kickstareter__text="To help realize our dream, we are asking the worldwide cosplay community to help us fund this incredible undertaking. In Spring 2021 we will officially launch a Kickstarter Campaign to secure funding and speed up the launch of this new platform. If you're interested in supporting our kickstarter or gaining early access to the platform, please sign up with your email below."
